    "title": "Looking for Real Estate Agent at 99acres",
    "description": "99acres has an exciting opening for a Real Estate Agent at our Madurai office. Join a company that values innovation, collaboration, and continuous learning.\n\nAbout 99acres:\n99acres is a leading organization in the Hybrid sector, committed to excellence, innovation, and employee growth. We offer a dynamic work environment where talent is recognized and rewarded.\n\nKey Responsibilities:\n• Conduct land acquisition due diligence and feasibility studies\n• Build relationships with channel partners and brokers\n• Source and close property deals with prospective buyers and investors\n• Liaise with banks and NBFCs for home loan assistance to customers\n• Manage relationships with existing customers post-purchase\n• Achieve monthly and quarterly sales targets\n• Conduct site visits and property presentations for clients\n\nRequired Skills & Qualifications:\n• Bachelor's degree in a relevant field\n• 1-3 years of relevant experience\n• Proficiency in Market Research\n• Proficiency in CRM Software\n• Proficiency in Title Search\n• Proficiency in GIS Tools\n• Proficiency in Due Diligence\n• Proficiency in Portfolio Management\n• Proficiency in Sales Techniques\n• Proficiency in MS Office\n\nWork Mode: Hybrid - Flexible work-from-home and office\n\nWhat We Offer:\n• Provident Fund and Gratuity as per company policy\n• Comprehensive health insurance for self and family\n• Transportation and conveyance allowance\n• International travel opportunities for senior roles\n• Learning & development budget\n• Competitive salary with performance-linked incentives\n• Salary Range: 4 LPA - 9 LPA per annum\n\nLocation: Madurai, Tamil Nadu, India\n\nIf you are excited about this opportunity, apply now and take the next step in your career journey with 99acres!",
